snippet.title: Hovercraft Race 3D - Now Avaible on App Store & Google Play
snippet.description:
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/hovercraft-race-3d/id1183878570
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jejnet.hover
Test your reflexes in this game endless runner futuristic! How far you are able to get there? You'll drive your hovercraft ever increasing speed you will need to dodge other players with quick lane changes.
Can you beat all the records?
